Release history for the doms-pidregistration project.

New entries are added at the top and should include the date for each release as well as mentioning new features
briefly.

1.0.8.4 released 2020-07-23
 * Rebuild code to Java 8
 * Update dependencies to latest versions
 * Change log framework from log4j to logback (via slf4j)
 * Fix code issues reported by forbiddenapis

1.0.8.3 released 2016-07-04
 * Change to jre7 edition of postgres JDBC driver - fixes broken 1.0.8.2 release

1.0.8.2 released 2016-07-04
 * Update postgres JDBC driver to newest version (9.4.1208)

1.0.8.1 relased 2015-09-15
 * Backport changes from 1.0.11 release: 
 ** Don't load certificate when in test mode
 ** Don't bundle along the certificate in the release package

1.0.8 released 2014-07-29
 * Added configurable timeout for DOMS WS connection
 * Handled that getIDsModified will return the same ID more than once if the object has been modified more than once since the given cutoff date

1.0.7 released 2013-11-12
 * Handled both behaviours of getIDsmodified (since seems to be either exclusive or inclusive depending on the environment)
 * Added timestamps for last object read in the database

1.0.6 released 2013-11-06
 * Added index to state

1.0.5 released 2013-11-04
 * Entity expansion error fixed by disabling entity expansion limit
 * Signature error fixed by updating handle client to v7.3.1

1.0.4 released 2013-10-31
 * Improved robustness of test mode
 * Can now handle a given number of objects to test in test mode

1.0.3 released 2013-10-24
 * Improved logging

1.0.2 released 2013-10-17
 * Changed the name of privateKeyPath property in conf template

1.0.1 released 2013-10-17
 * Assembly copies private key to conf

1.0.0 released 2013-10-17
 * Initial release.
